    "Moreover, the calculation cost of the specialized outlier removal module is high, so it cannot be applied to real scenes in real-time.",
    "To this end, researchers have proposed a series of new methods for partially overlapping point clouds.",
    "Reject non-overlapping regions Sarode et al. (2020) proposed a full convolutional neural network MaskNet.",
    "Perform learn-based inner estimation based on the PointNet structure.",
    "The network is trained to identify which points in the target point cloud are internal by calculating masks, so that these points and the source point cloud closely describe the same part of the object/scene geometry."
